name: Kitsune in the Grass
description: In Japanese folklore the Kitsune was considered a supernatural being capable of shape shifting into a human form. Depicted with 9 tails and 8 purple praying mantis heads, the Kitsune of my imagination is a combination of the Western Hydra and the Eastern fox spirit. Thank you to bimoded60 on BlendSwap for the gorgeous Ghibli background.
